> when im presenting this project as a demo to my professor, how can i show SSO 

â— Great question! For a university demo, here are several ways to effectively demonstrate SSO (Single Sign-On) in your project:

  1. Visual Architecture Diagram (Recommended Start)

  Before the live demo, prepare a simple diagram showing:
